===================STAR WARS SHIPFIGTHER===================
You must destroy most of the ships than you can to prevent
the enemy to fight.

To destroy the ships, click on it with the mouse.

To pause the game, press the Escape key.

You gain a level when you shoot ten ships. Each level
resets your health bar.

The game ends when the red lightsaber -your health bar-
become empty.
===========================================================
